p: A platform appeared from the past!
There seems to be another old page torn from a
notebook. Should you read through it?
\b"As I climbed higher to the top, a very strange screech from a few floors above caught my attention."
There seems to be an old page torn from a notebook.
\b"This tower seems to have been falling apart over
the last few years. Had it not been for the sound of
fluttering above me, I may have turned around."
\b"The sound of being so close to a big
discovery pushed me ever forward. I can't walk away now!"
